      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! It honestly breaks my heart a little to let this beauty go, but she\u2019s ready for a new home where she\u2019ll be just as pampered as she was with me. I\u2019ve kept her tucked away in a climate-controlled garage, and honestly, you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish. She drives like a dream and looks like she just rolled off the showroom floor. If you're looking for that perfect, 'treat yourself' ride that\u2019s been loved every mile of the way, this is the one. Come by, have a coffee, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
