      "description": "Offered is a meticulously sorted example for the discerning driver who demands mechanical synchronicity. This chassis exhibits zero cowl shake, and the powertrain operates with surgical precision. The compression ratios across all cylinders are within factory-spec tolerances, ensuring a linear torque curve and crisp throttle tip-in. I\u2019ve performed a comprehensive fluid service using high-viscosity synthetic lubricants to ensure optimal thermal management under load. The suspension geometry has been professionally aligned to eliminate bump steer, while the bushings remain compliant yet firm for communicative feedback. This is a turn-key, high-performance machine with a drivetrain that feels as tight as the day it left the assembly line. No leaks, no lash in the differential, just pure mechanical harmony.",
